title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.04.08
description:
STEVE TO THE RESCUE: THE BEGINNING:
 -----------------------------------
    It is time to look back at how it all started! We look at some of the first episodes of "Steve to the Rescue". Steve talks about a couple different episodes...including one with a 14 year-old prostitute! We also look at one of the first abusive boyfriends that Steve had to deal with. Plus... Two viewers wanted to take their enjoyment of the show to the next level, so after writing in to Steve, they&#039;re here to get their very own Steve hairdos!
